Dallas Morning News</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">11 May</span> 2007</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Having+a+ball+with+knitting&amp;rft.pub=%27%27The+Dallas+Morning+News%27%27&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.au=Sarah+Kerner&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dallasnews.com%2Fsharedcontent%2Fdws%2Ffea%2Fsolutions%2Fstories%2FDN-nso_knitting_0417liv.State.Edition1.75c246d.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASweater+curse\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-manning_2003-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-manning_2003_3-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-manning_2003_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-manning_2003_3-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-manning_2003_3-3\"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-manning_2003_3-4\"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Manning, Tara Jon (2003). <i>Men in Knits: Sweaters to Knit that He WILL Wear</i>. Loveland, Colorado: Interweave Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-931499-23-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1-931499-23-3\">1-931499-23-3</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Men+in+Knits%3A+Sweaters+to+Knit+that+He+WILL+Wear&amp;rft.place=Loveland%2C+Colorado&amp;rft.pub=Interweave+Press&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.isbn=1-931499-23-3&amp;rft.aulast=Manning&amp;rft.aufirst=Tara+Jon&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASweater+curse\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-knitlits